-- Israeli Drones Used by Turkish Armed Forces to Locate PKK, Sabah Reports
-- Steve Bryant
-- 2010-07-02T05:24:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-02/israeli-drones-used-by-turkish-armed-forces-to-locate-pkk-sabah-reports.html

          
          
             Turkey’s Armed Forces used Israeli 
technology to locate and kill 12 members of the Kurdistan 
Workers’ Party in southeast Turkey, Sabah newspaper reported.  
 Israeli "Heron" unmanned planes spotted the PKK members and
helped guide U.S.-made Cobra helicopter gunships to their 
location in Siirt province yesterday, the newspaper said, 
without saying how it got the information.  
